Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.79,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:17.73,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地變得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:23.14,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,背後彷彿有你的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:30.09,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,追趕了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:41.20,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我頻頻回頭看著你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:51.30,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,新戀情的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.41,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,是兩人在不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:07.19,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,展開看不見的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.36,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永遠不願分離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.61,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓我只愛你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我又毀滅了一個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我好不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易跟我喜歡的人告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想跟我喜歡的人\N一起做好多好多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不會死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用世界上的任何武器\N恐怕都無法…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，沒有人能殺得了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也沒有人能阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有個老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很怕寂寞\N常常讓我很頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說，她是個很難伺候\N很麻煩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管如此，我還是很愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我會死在這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許已經不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說，我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見我心愛的女人\N把她擁在懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能活著，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有心愛的男人，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把它記住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記住那些被我毀掉的\N城鎮的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定曾經有很多人\N在那裏生活過的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算努力把它記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概沒有人能夠原諒\N我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望老天爺至少\N允許我擁有這兩個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}#05 謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動詞的五段活用有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定形，連用形，終止形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連體形，假設形，命令形…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼白日夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你個頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地…地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是趕快…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快去避難比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說等警報鈴聲響了\N才開始避難演習的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼討厭我的課嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師，我尿急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼了，修…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，慢一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑太快了啦，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是轟炸嗎？還是飛彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，什麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你，你先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是男女朋友耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃當然一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，危險的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，來的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個很大的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且性能還不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一把這麼大的地震\N誤當作是被攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我會做出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，不要看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是她的男朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來只受損了這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毀掉這所學校\N也是輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是看到了\N什麼很可怕的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？地震呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是因為剛才那件事\N使我的身體某處故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對於千瀨的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你說，剛才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我錯誤啟動了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很遲鈍\N總是會做出危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我現在已經\N稍微能控制力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才也只稍微爆炸一下\N就控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過相對的，我好像故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你說了\N不要跟我道歉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回去吧，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟他們一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去，我會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是武器，所以需要維修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像人類需要吃藥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好整修一下\N我會沒命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了，明天學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會變得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是誰害你受這種苦的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那個老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是把你的身體\N改造成這樣的成員之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你還要聽這種人的話？\N那個…可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你不會不甘心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，我還有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上到展望台來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等你來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨和修次還在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次他…修次他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個班級點名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，原來你平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受了一點傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升機送她去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊，那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個到哪裏去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你們這種自私的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事的時候\N只會給大家帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什麼眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙\N也是靠千瀨在保護著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部到齊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我不是存心要打你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一時衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，明美，大家都很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，我打算休學去加入軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保護一個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論這個世界發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想保護這個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我一直以來的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保護明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡，你跟我表白有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好羨慕小淳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的四周\N好多人事物都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（緊急出動）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在死之前\N沒有感到痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得你好像是青森人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏離千瀨的地域蠻近的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片你帶著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鐵小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨妹妹…今天沒來\N是不是去約會了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就不要跟她分手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在還是很喜歡她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊，中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如讓千瀨殺死算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以把一切\N都推給那孩子承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還只是個高中生女孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我們要死得這麼痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千瀨殺死時\N一點痛苦都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣好像有點賴皮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今後這個星球會更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千瀨的口頭禪傳染了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要等我喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次我一定會赴約的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在關東一帶的戰況是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣亂來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經透過衛星得知戰況了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒有按照我的指示行動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻出動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這樣下去\N戰況會越來越慘烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在展望台等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友現在不在展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據監視部隊傳來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不准對我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一眨眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回神過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是孤伶伶一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我軍部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去的話，一定會死更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是死的不是我認識的\N不是我喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取而代之的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些注定要\N被我殺的人死掉罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說，有什麼不同呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是一樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了只會讓我更難過痛苦以外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們讓我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…我的男朋友在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少，今天一天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想在這個城市殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼阿修沒有來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？是情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修的監視記錄？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想聽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬美學姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點來啊，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說\N你有很多話要跟我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有很多很多話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不談戀愛了\N我不知道會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有味道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就這樣，一直待到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後，千瀨慢慢的開口說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:43.46,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.45,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,難以入眠的夜裏總不停的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:59.63,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺黎明已悄然到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.98,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼想聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:13.15,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,對你的思念越來越強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.09,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,淚水奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:30.26,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:36.50,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍無法忘懷你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.38,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.91,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:52.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是千瀨的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這麼喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終兵器彼女下一回\N「同學」

